   Health topics by subject area

        * Diabetes
          Includes publications on medications, nutrition, preventing
          complications, and more.
        * Digestive diseases
          Includes publications on hepatitis, diagnostic tests, ulcers,
          gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD), gas, constipation, and
          more.
        * Endocrine and metabolic diseases
          Includes publications on Cushing's disease, Addison's disease, and
          more.
        * Hemotologic (blood) diseases
          Includes publications on hemochromatosis and thrombocytopenic
          purpura.
        * Kidney diseases
          Includes publications on kidney stones, dialysis, nutrition, kidney
          failure (end-stage renal disease), and more.
        * Nutrition
          Includes information on diabetes nutrition, renal nutrition,
          general nutrition, and more.
        * Urologic diseases
          Includes publications on impotence, interstitial cystitis, urinary
          tract infections, bladder control, and more.
        * Weight loss and control
          Includes publications on eating disorders, exercise, dieting,
          surgery, and more.

   Spanish-language publications

        * Spanish translations of our most popular fact sheets.
          Includes links to other foreign-language health information
          resources.

   Easy-to-read publications

        * Easy-to-read booklets, rich in illustrations, covering a variety of
          topics.

   Statistics

        * U.S. statistics from NIDDK, plus links to other sources.

   Publications lists and order forms

        * Order printed copies using these forms.
          Note: Online versions may be more recently updated than printed
          copies.

   Combined Health Information Database (CHID)

        * Search this database of hard-to-find health education media in 17
          subject areas. Includes a detailed search form for finding
          foreign-language health education materials.

   Directories of Professional and Voluntary Organizations

        * Diabetes
        * Digestive Diseases (for patients)
        * Digestive Diseases (for professionals)
        * Endocrine and Metabolic Diseases
        * Kidney and Urologic Diseases
        * Obesity, Weight Control, and Nutrition

   Clinical Practice Guidelines

        * Comprehensive database of evidence-based clinical practice
          guidelines and related documents.

